cs.CV, cs.GR, cs.MM, cs.RO, cs.AI. 

This paper involves computer vision techniques for reconstructing a 3D time-lapse video sequence from a collection of internet photos. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The paper also deals with graphics (cs.GR) and multimedia (cs.MM) aspects, as well as robotics (cs.RO) for camera motion. Finally, the paper involves some level of artificial intelligence (cs.AI) for solving the technical challenges mentioned in the abstract.
